               <p>Cross Examination.</p>
               <p>You are not all very particular to lock your doors? - Yes; we are, because we don't know one another; I saw him take the apartments of Mr. Cockman as I was fetching up water; they moved in at four in the morning; I heard a noise and got up to see what was the matter, and saw the cart of goods at the door.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17780715-88-person795">
