                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>Mr. Carty and I searched the room in the house the last witness lives in, which she calls a parlour; Carty said what place is this under the stairs? Carleton then gave him a key out of his pocket, Mr. Carty went in and found a hanger and a pistol under the stairs going up by his room door; we found nothing in the parlour; the pistol was loaded three fingers deep.</p>
